Depends: git, python, asciibanner, apkeditor, apksigner
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/Anon4You/PKiller
Description: Automated PairIP License Removal Tool for Android APKs
 PKiller is an automated tool designed to remove PairIP license
 protection from Android APK files. Streamlines the process of
 bypassing PairIP security for security research and analysis.
